com.foreach.imageserver.core.business

Class ImageModification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.imageserver.core.business.ImageModification
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.springframework.data.domain.Persistable<ImageModificationId>

    @Entity
public class ImageModification
extends Object
implements org.springframework.data.domain.Persistable<ImageModificationId>, Serializable
    The ImageModification specifies how an original image is to be transformed into an image conforming to a specific ImageResolution.

    Note that an ImageModification is generic; the non-generic options required for an actual transform are specified using an ImageVariant object.
